Piggybacking on this issue (let me know if it's better suited as a separate one). I changed gen_file_list.sh, ran it and then attempted building again, now I'm instead getting the following:

```
Undefined symbols for architecture x86_64:
  "_deflate", referenced from:
      tensorflow::io::ZlibOutputBuffer::Deflate(int) in zlib_outputbuffer.o
  "_deflateEnd", referenced from:
      tensorflow::io::ZlibOutputBuffer::Close() in zlib_outputbuffer.o
  "_deflateInit2_", referenced from:
      tensorflow::io::ZlibOutputBuffer::ZlibOutputBuffer(tensorflow::WritableFile*, int, int, tensorflow::io::ZlibCompressionOptions const&) in zlib_outputbuffer.o
  "_inflate", referenced from:
      tensorflow::io::ZlibInputBuffer::Inflate() in zlib_inputbuffer.o
  "_inflateEnd", referenced from:
      tensorflow::io::ZlibInputBuffer::~ZlibInputBuffer() in zlib_inputbuffer.o
  "_inflateInit2_", referenced from:
      tensorflow::io::ZlibInputBuffer::ZlibInputBuffer(tensorflow::RandomAccessFile*, unsigned long, unsigned long, tensorflow::io::ZlibCompressionOptions const&) in zlib_inputbuffer.o
ld: symbol(s) not found for architecture x86_64
clang: error: linker command failed with exit code 1 (use -v to see invocation)
make: *** [/Users/albhaf/src/github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/gen/host_bin/proto_text] Error 1
+ '[' 2 -ne 0 ']'
+ echo 'armv7 compilation failed.'
armv7 compilation failed.
+ exit 1
```
